# Laravel Upgrade Guide

## When to use

- Upgrading Laravel from one version to another (5.x through 13.x)
- Handling breaking changes between Laravel versions
- Updating composer.json dependencies for a new Laravel release
- Migrating deprecated features (routes, middleware, config) to new patterns

## Keywords

`laravel upgrade`, `laravel/framework`, `breaking changes`, `migration`, `10.x`, `11.x`, `12.x`, `13.x`, `artisan --version`, `composer update`
